    <comment>- update to 0.1.2.2:
  * A bug-fix minor release.
  * Fix invalid Unicode escape sequences in byte strings
  * A very minor 'between-patches' release adding support for
    python versions 3.9+.
  * Improved logging for HTMLRTF stripping.
  * Added transform_based_on_content_type.
  * Correctly handle hex arrays in text extraction.</comment>
